transcripts: This is the Chef's Choice Waffle Cone Express available at Bed Bath and Beyond. Indulge in your favorite ice cream and frozen yogurt treats with home style waffle cones made right in your kitchen. The Chef's Choice Waffle Cone Express lets you create freshly backed cones in just two minutes or less in a variety of sizes with color select controls with lighter and darker finishes you're homemade waffle cone cooks perfectly and evenly to your liking. Just use the included cone form and roll with a towel to safely handle the hot waffle. The cones stand up in any narrow glass making them easy to fill and serve. Features include the built in cord storage which allows you to conveniently stow the machine upright and out of sight saving precious counter space. Plus your waffle cone express come with a handy recipe book to create the batter necessary to make the cones. Treat yourself with the Chef's Choice Waffle Cone Express available online.
